reviewText: I would of liked more songs fore the money
This is and advertisement piece of 6 songs. All are on Homecoming videos. Waste of money.
Great songs and singing.  I was disappointed in how many songs were on this.  10 is not enough for the price
The video that I received called "At The Cross" was just fine. I discovered it was more of a "Sample" of the Gaither videos but I liked it just the same; just was not long enough.
